<para style="q1">

<verse number="16" style="v" />Come and listen, all you who fear God,</para>

<para style="q1">and I will declare what he has done for my soul.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="17" style="v" />I cried to him with my mouth,</para>

<para style="q1">and he was praised with my tongue.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="18" style="v" />If I had seen sin within my heart,</para>

<para style="q1">the Lord would not have listened to me.</para>
